"AliQuick - AliExpress Image Downloader" allows you to download AliExpress images and description to your computer.
It's free, give it a try!

How to Download Product Images:
1. Install the extension by clicking the “Add to chrome” button.
2. Open an AliExpress product page.
3.Select the product.
4.Then Click on the download buttons.

It's as simple as that!

Free tool for downloading images and description from AliExpress. You will see the buttons for download on AliExpress product pages.
